 Create Vega-Lite specifications in Elm. A specification can be sent to a
Vega-Lite runtime to generate the graphics. While this is a pure Elm package, to
generate the graphical output you probably want to send the JSON generated by
`toVegaLite` via a port to some JavaScript that invokes the Vega-Lite runtime.
Alternatively, to avoid coding the link to the Vega-Lite runtime, you can embed
specifications directly in a [litvis document](https://github.com/gicentre/litvis).


